setting custom font size
----------------------------

create a file ~/.Xresources

xterm*faceName: Monospace
xterm*faceSize: 12

save
and run 
$ xrdb -merge ~/.Xresources

extra configs

visualBell: Boolean
xterm*background: COLOR
xterm*foreground: COLOR
xterm*poinercolor: COLOR

VISIT FOR MORE: https://how-to.fandom.com/wiki/How_to_configure_xterm
